Package org.opendaylight.controller.switchmanager

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IInventoryListener
    Primary purpose of this interface is to provide methods to listen to inventory changes
    ISpanAware
    The interface provides the methods for notifying when span ports are configured/unconfigured.
    ISwitchManager
    Primary purpose of this interface is to provide methods for application to access various system resources and inventory data including nodes, node connectors and their properties, Layer3 configurations, Span configurations, node configurations, network device representations viewed by Controller Web applications.
    ISwitchManagerAware
    The interface provides methods to notify listeners about subnet and mode changes.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SpanConfig
    The class represents a Span Port configuration for a network node.
    Subnet
    The class describes subnet information including L3 address, vlan and set of ports associated with the subnet.
    SubnetConfig
    The class represents a subnet configuration.
    SubnetConfigTest  
    SubnetTest  
    Switch
    The class describes switch related information including L2 address, ports, span ports and associated node representation
    SwitchConfig
    The class describes a switch configuration as a collection of properties
    SwitchTest
